w21zb47cxq.name: Al-Firdaus Mosque
w21zb47cxq.remarks: This old generation masjid located in the West, off Choa Chu Kang road, was built in 1962. In 1999, the masjid, which serves the needs of the nearby residents, was rebuilt. Today, it can accommodate up to 200 people.Â  There are religious classes for adults in the evening.
